manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: EZ COZY 16 Pack Garage Hooks - Keep Things Organized and Make Life Easier The heavy duty garage hooks are made of sturdy steel material, and covered with rubber to protect your things from scratching or falling down. The garage wall hooks can be used in garage, shed, warehouse, garden, shop and barn.

The set of garage hangers are designed to organize your bikes, ladders, garden tools, power tools, shovel, broom, or bulk items. You can make full use of wall space and save more space for other items with this utility hooks for garage.
Equipped with two types of screws and anchors, the garage storage hooks can be easily installed on various walls with only an electric drill and a screwdriver, keeping everything in order.
There are multiple sizes of garage hangers to fit all of your needs ranging from items as big as bicycles to the smaller ones like extension cord, perfect for hanging garden tools.

Do the hooks need to be mounted into studs? No, they can be mounted into drywall or concrete with the included anchors. Will these hooks rust over time? What color are the garage organization hooks? The wall hooks come in a bright orange color for high visibility in the garage. What is the weight capacity of each hangar? It is in the listing. Depends on which hook and how it is attached to the wall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and stable hooks
reviews.reviewText: I have a lot of things to hang in my house, that way I can be more organized, and these look like they'll do the trick for more than half of the things I need to take care of. There's a pair of smaller hooks, and just one of them works perfectly for my ironing board which used to have to sit on the floor. The size range of these hooks, plus the anchors that come with them mean you can hang a large variety of objects, from bicycles, to yard tools (weed eaters as example) and many other items. I do find that many of these have narrow spaces between the hooks but that's why they come in pairs, so they can be utilized to lay items across if necessary. The narrowness of some of the hooks is why I took down one star, I'd like a larger variety of hooks that have a wider space for items to fit into when hung up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Versatile collection of hooks
reviews.reviewText: These hooks are serving their purpose in my shed for storing a large variety of the many tools we have collected over many years. Hubby was very adept at fixing nearly everything himself and building whatever we might need. We have a lot of miscellaneous tools that these brackets handle quite well. The large variety of shapes and sizes of the hooks and brackets lend themselves to versatile use. Every thing is easy to see, so there is no digging through cupboards, boxes or bins to find what is needed. The brackets are very easy to attach to studs or a wall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These seem like quality hooks, selection is a bit repetitive
reviews.reviewText: I like the look of these hooks. They look premium. I can't speak to how well the rubber coating will stand up over time, but they look great out of the box.As usual, the mounting hardware is useless. At the very least, the screws have the wrong type of head on them. I always use better quality hardware that I keep on hand for these sorts of things.The variety of hooks is a bit repetitive. You basically get two sizes of the one shape and three sizes of the other shape. They are not bad selections, but they are pretty basic. I didn't take any stars off for this, but I thought about it.(I've never used this style of broom hooks. I'm more than leery of them and doubt I'll end up hanging them on the wall.)
